## 4. Experiment Registry

Every experiment — planned or complete — must have an entry in:

**`experiments/EXPERIMENT_REGISTRY.md`**

### When creating a new experiment, Cursor must add a registry row with:

```markdown
| EXP-NN | <Topic> | `experiments/<category>/<folder>/` | <one-sentence hypothesis> | 📋 Planned | — | <next question> |
```

### Status must be updated as work progresses:

```
📋 Planned → 🔄 In Progress → ✅ Complete
```

Cursor must also update `experiments/EXPERIMENT_DASHBOARD.md` with the new experiment entry under the correct section.

